*Sunca* se već povukla iza oblaka (The sun already disappeared behind the clouds).
Mnogi ljudi se sunčaju na plaži (*Sunca* se) (Many people are sunbathing on the beach).
Uživajući u *suncu* se može lako prehladiti (Enjoying the sun, one can easily catch a cold).
Dolazak *sunca* donosi sreću (The arrival of the sun brings happiness).